snippet.title: MapleStory iTCG online gameplay
snippet.description:
Video provided by Nexon, published with permission.

MapleStory iTCG Online draws on the characters, weapons, monsters and magic of MapleStory to create the ultimate online collectable card game experience. Each time you play, you'll choose a MapleStory hero to represent you in a fight to the finish. Youll duel your friends, build new decks, devise new strategies and take part in exciting tournaments all to become the iTCG master!

MapleStory is a free-to-play, 2D, side-scrolling massively multiplayer online role-playing game.

Published by Nexon America Inc.
Developed by Wizet
Release date: Nov 28, 2006
Platform: Windows
